## CLI

| Command | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `creation serve` | Local UI at `:8787` |
| `creation run --idea "…" --agent codex` | Headless full loop with live phase output |
| `creation run --verbose` | Stream agent CLI lines during the build |
| `creation run --demo` | Full pipeline without live API keys |
| `creation doctor` | Verify keys, Composio connections, 43 agents on PATH |
| `creation projects` | List local projects |
| `creation portfolio` | Portfolio health summary |
| `creation queue-add <id>` | Queue project for batch / overnight run |
| `creation queue-run` | Run next queued project |
| `creation schedule --enable` | Enable periodic scheduler (default every 24h) |
| `creation pitch` | Advanced: Stripe SDK preset via CLI (12 turns) |

